    "description": "Fujipream Corporation engages in the precision laminating and high-functional composite materials business in Japan and internationally. It operates through two segments: Precision Laminating and High-Performance Composite Materials, and Environmental Living Space and Engineering. The Precision Laminating and High-Performance Composite Materials segment produces touch panel sensor substrates and components for liquid crystal displays, as well as manufactures and sells automotive parts. The Environmental Living Space and Engineering segment includes solar cell modules, solar power generation system-related products, insulation generation systems, and film-laminated glass for thermal insulation and shatter-proofing. This segment also engages in the sale of packaging and wrapping materials and is involved in logistics-related operations and mechatronics businesses. The company was incorporated in 1982 and is headquartered in Himeji, Japan."
